{"title_page": "Electoral district of Whitsunday", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=August 2019}}\n{{Infobox Australian Electorate |name     = Whitsunday\n|federal=|state    = qld\n|upper=|image    = ECQ-2017-Final-Whitsunday.pdf\n|caption  = Electoral map of Whitsunday 2017\n|lifespan =\n|mp       = [[Jason Costigan]]\n|mp-party = [[North Queensland First]]\n|namesake = [[Whitsunday Island]]\n|electors = 32156\n|electors_year = 2015\n|area     = 27761\n|class    =\n|coordinates = {{coord|20|35|S|149|2|E|type:adm2nd|display=inline,title}}\n| near-n             = ''[[Coral Sea]]''\n| near-ne            = ''[[Coral Sea]]''\n| near-e             = ''[[Coral Sea]]''\n| near-se            = [[Electoral district of Mackay|Mackay]]\n| near-s             = [[Electoral district of Mirani|Mirani]]\n| near-sw            = [[Electoral district of Mirani|Mirani]]\n| near-w             = [[Electoral district of Burdekin|Burdekin]]\n| near-nw            = [[Electoral district of Burdekin|Burdekin]]\n}}\n[[File:QLD - Whitsunday 2008.png|thumb|Electoral map of Whitsunday 2008]]\n'''Whitsunday''' is an electoral division in the [[Legislative Assembly of Queensland]], [[Queensland]], Australia.\n\nIt extends from the northern suburbs of [[Mackay, Queensland|Mackay]] to [[Bowen, Queensland|Bowen]] and [[Proserpine, Queensland|Proserpine]] as well as east to the [[Whitsunday Islands]].\n\n==Members for Whitsunday==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!\n!Member\n!Party affiliation\n!Period\n|-\n| {{Australian party style|Nationals QLD}}|&nbsp;\n| [[Lloyd Roberts (politician)|Lloyd Roberts]]\n| [[National Party of Australia \u2013 Queensland|Country Party]]\n| 1950\u20131961\n|-\n| {{Australian party style|Nationals QLD}}|&nbsp;\n|rowspan=\"2\"| [[Ron Camm]]\n| [[National Party of Australia \u2013 Queensland|Country]]\n| 1961\u20131974\n|-\n| {{Australian party style|Nationals QLD}}|&nbsp;\n| [[National Party of Australia \u2013 Queensland|National]]\n| 1974\u20131980\n|-\n| {{Australian party